# Clean Architecture

## Layer Structure

```
lib/
├── data/           # APIs, local storage, repository implementations
├── domain/         # entities, params, repository interfaces, use cases
├── presentation/   # blocs, screens, common widgets, routes
├── core/           # dio, config, utils, use case base
├── constants/      # colors, theme, text, network constants
└── di/             # GetIt service locator
```

## Import Rules

- `domain/` MUST NOT import from `data/` or `presentation/`
- `data/` may import `domain/` and `core/` only
- `presentation/` may import `domain/` and `core/` only — never `data/` directly
- `core/` and `constants/` are shared by all layers

## Feature Creation Order

1. Entity in `domain/entities/`
2. Params in `domain/params/`
3. Repository interface in `domain/repository_interfaces/`
4. API interface + impl in `data/data_sources/remote/apis/`
5. Repository impl in `data/repository/`
6. Use case(s) in `domain/usecases/`
7. BLoC in `presentation/blocs/`
8. Screen in `presentation/screens/`
9. Register DI in all three layer modules
10. Add route to `presentation/routes/app_routes.dart` and the matching route module
